description:
A library of utilities usable across all types of .NET applications (WPF, WinForms, ASP.NET, console, service, etc.). Available utilities are: XmlUtilities, AssemblyUtilities, IOUtilities, ConvertUtilities, JsonUtilities, CommandLineUtilities, WizardForm, RibbonControl, DockPanel, EditableUri, BitsServer, NtfsAlternateStream, ZipFile, UITypeEditors, TypeConverters, ChunkedMemoryStream, ContentType, Country, CustomThreadPool, Crc16, Crc32, DistinctDictionary, AutoObject, GrammaticalNumberConverter, CompoundFile, ScriptEngine, PerceivedType, RtfReader, JobObject, Authenticode, Privilege, Template Engine and more! Visit the product page for more information!

The CodeFluent Entities Blog : http://blog.codefluententities.com/
The CodeFluent Entities Blog - Exploring the CodeFluent Runtime series : http://blog.codefluententities.com/category/exploring-the-codefluent-runtime/
